The Azuma Shopping app lets you shop millions 
of products and manage your Azuma orders from 
anywhere. Browse, shop by department, compare prices, 
read reviews, share products with friends, and check the 
status of your orders.
Compare prices and availability by typing in your search,You have full access to your Shopping Cart, Wish 
Lists, payment and Prime shipping options, just like on the
 full Amazon.com site. All Azuma Shopping app purchases 
are routed through  secure servers to encrypt and
 safeguard your personal information.

Future Features:
scanning a barcode or an image with your camera, or using 
your voice.
You can also sign-up for 
shipment/delievery notifications to know when your order ships and 
arrives.
Subscribe & Save order history, and 1-Click settings.
